Amstel king tree 🤝 Coconut Merlot planter

This tree likes a bright space and to be watered when the top inches of soil dries out. One of my favourites! 

Also shoutout to the little ZZ plant in the matte pink sphere we did as well 🥹
It feels like Christmas in here with all our new plants! 😍

Starting the New Year with this lovely set! 

If you’re looking for a replacement for your Christmas Tree then come check out all our XL trees and pots in store 🤍

Plant and wine night is back!  Check our website under ‘Terrarium workshop’ for more details and tickets. 
🤍

We loved planting up this indoor garden box today ☺️. The client wanted XL fiddle leaf figs surrounded by tropical plants. It turned out so lush! 💚
I didn’t video the 20 trips it took to empty out 200lbs of rock before 😂😅
Have you been to @tolivefor.bakery yet?  It is one of our favourite vegan cafes! They have the best croissants and serve deeelicious lattes. Thanks for letting us add green babies ☺️🌱💚

Bird of paradise 🤝 sphere planter 

I love this set up so much especially in our clients lovely home!

❤️‍🔥 Valentines plant + wine night ❤️‍🔥 is happening at the Jungle! 

Come with your partner, mama or best friend to handcraft a growing gift for each other. Each couple will build each other a terrarium to take home that will grow and flourish over the years. 

Space is limited so grab your ticket online at wcjungle.com 🫶

Absolutely love these plants in our clients beautiful home! 

We delivered these plants all the way to Kamloops to make this magic happen 🪄🌱
Describe your perfect day 🫶

The ficus is potted in our coconut white merlot planter and the cactus is in our low dish planter.

Do you know someone who loves plants and happy hour? Give them the gift of a “Wine + Plant night”! 
This workshop is a great way to sip on vino or mocktails while creating your own mini jungle terrarium to take home.
Cheers to a fun and unique experience! 🥂🪴

Tickets available on our website under “gift cards”
